{"tid":2130670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本向越南貸款366.6億日元 建6艘巡邏艦","createTime":"2020-07-29T10:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T17:40:07.000Z","uid":75656,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"45eb106c173c240a11aaa81bd3a0f8d8afca3547","tid":2130670,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:50:14.000Z","msg":"在南海局勢緊張之際，越南28日與日本國際協力機構（JICA）簽署了一項協議，向日本借貸366.3億日元（約新台幣102億元）建造6艘巡邏艦。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，越南當地媒體指出，這6艘艦艇將在2025年10月交付越南海岸防衛隊，將有助於提升越南的海上防衛能力；越南共產黨官方報也指出，這6艘船隻將用於加強執法和海上救援行動，確保越南的主權，海上安全和航行自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3242602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3242602&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=f6588b2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3242602&h=a82c4271\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3242602</a>"},{"pid":"f97ea3d379e8dc9da9a13c67c7eb5d979c8c273c","tid":2130670,"uid":317979,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZKMmr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZKMmr8.jpg&h=9e5c6f86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eed8cdf1b4c0509ab51ba2cb8c456ab81f369092","tid":2130670,"uid":259732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de06c9a535450f572d43f80955cc7d98929f8714","tid":2130670,"uid":23086,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"標題掉轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d2d5dc6a951bf47aef5d6298f515843b45fa94","tid":2130670,"uid":242119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"你標題?"}